    <!-- Accessibility Prompt -->
    <string name="accessibility_requirement_title">ACCESSIBILITY PERMISSION REQUIRED</string>
    <string name="accessibility_requirement_desc">Why does Key Viewer need this permission?\n\nThe system (especially Game Turbo) often automatically blocks touch-through when it detects a full-screen overlay on top of the game.\n\nTo draw smooth real-time \'Touch points\' and allow you to touch through without lag, the app needs to use the display privileges of Accessibility.\n\n🔒 PRIVACY COMMITMENT:\nThe app does not read screen content or collect personal data. This permission is used solely for drawing touch point graphics.</string>
